file.name: openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: gosrvlibexample
  description: Public API
  contact:
    email: dev@example.com
  license:
    name: Internal use only. All rights reserved.
    url: 'https://github.com/gosrvlibexample/gosrvlibexample/blob/main/LICENSE'
  version: 1.0.0
servers:
  - url: 'https://gosrvlibexample:8071/'
tags:
  - name: ping
    description: Ping this service
  - name: uid
    description: generate a random UID
paths:
  /ping:
    get:
      tags:
        - ping
      summary: Check if the service is reachable
      responses:
        '200':
          description: The service is reachable
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                type: string
                description: OK
  /uid:
    get:
      tags:
        - uid
      summary: Generates a random UID
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Random UID
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: string
                description: UID

Error: notImplemented: path "/ping": get: responses: 200: contents: unsupported content types: [text/plain]
